Encoding: UTF-8
Package: xmpdf
Type: Package
Title: Add metadata to media files
Version: 0.1.0-0
Description: Add bookmarks and docinfo to pdf files.
             Can detect and use either 'pdftk' or 'ghostscript' commands.
             Can calculate and add appropriate bookmarks when merging multiple pdf files.
